OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHead teachers call for     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FOfsted to be replaced      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Teachers and head teachers handed a    
OL,6, petition to the government on Thursday,
OL,7, calling for Ofsted to be replaced.     
OL,9,FThe petition was started before head   
OL,10,Fteacher Ruth Perry took her own life   
OL,11,Fwhile waiting for an Ofsted report.    
OL,13,FMs Perry's family have blamed her death
OL,14,Fon the "intolerable pressure" of the   
OL,15,Finspection, which downgraded her       
OL,16,Fprimary school to "inadequate".        
OL,18,FThe Department for Education says      
OL,19,Finspections are "hugely important" and 
OL,20,F"a legal requirement".                 
